<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦ - <span class="c2">(١٩٨٠)</span> وَقَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5695">ابْنُ عَبْدِ الْأَعْلَى </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6257">الْمُعْتَمِرُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2609">أَبِيهِ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/0">بَعْضُ مَنْ كَانَ مَعِي </a>أَنَّهُ سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a>يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">« كَانَ خَمْرَهُمْ يَوْمَئِذٍ »</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>